{
  "stem": "2226.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A Jewish fellow couldn't get a license, or liquor, or tobacco, sugar-- you couldn't get a license for that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even we had two trucks like cartage trucks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't even get the license for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to go to a German for that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You pay him so much a month.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because he had the license, we could use his license.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like, here, here are some trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Hoffman has  owned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Passman has owned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Hoffman is dead a long time ago.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he's got the license.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You use his license and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1933 after the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We never could I-- did America know it was going to happen like this?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did you believe that they were going to burn live people?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Live children?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like, we had trucks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we knew a couple days before the airplanes come.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's ours, the Polacks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's ours, ours.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We gonna kill the Germans in no time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in the meantime, the Germans was already in the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We took the trucks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we ran away to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we come to Warsaw on the road, the Polacks stopped us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were already-- they were not Polacks, Polacks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were half German like Volkdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know what you call them here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You call them here Volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Like--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German descent.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And finally we got to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- I was over there for six days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I don't know if you remember, there used to be a General Sikorski, Sikorski, general.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he come the 6th of September.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, all Jewish young people should run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I took the-- the truck, and we had a family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was supposed to go to a near city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I took the truck with a family.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
